Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:36.34,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(580,300)}永不結束的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれそうな夢の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:11.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}よろこびを探す世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:22.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな輝きで　明日へと跳ぶの？　教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:27.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}声になった未来の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:33.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まりの my melody 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:39.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY！ 空が青く高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:44.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙ぐんだ今を忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:50.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひたすら進もうと誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かりあった瞬間は大切な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:58.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}ずっと一緒に　君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:12.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:17.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:23.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:31.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:05.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:11.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:22.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:33.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:39.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:44.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:50.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:58.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:12.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:17.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:23.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:31.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:27.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:32.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:37.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:42.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:47.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:57.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:03.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:08.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:16.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:27.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:36.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:27.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我手牽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:32.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:37.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一日又隨著斜陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:42.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆般漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:47.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:57.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:08.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:16.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:27.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:36.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該在旅館…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  今天變成了昨天  今天是試鏡日  今天是昨天  昨天是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  今天是昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（試鏡）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了  你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（優香: 快點過來！  啊, 帶好行李啊！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  起的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了  發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都在下田  日期也變回到昨天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海燒退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經退了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是退燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我離開家的時候媽媽對我說「加油啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天媽媽是對我說「一路順風」的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可能是第二次的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  也就是說我今晚又要發燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去買點藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不  我不是指的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  紗季  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神石！  不過我們也沒有許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  這可是個機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕佳良機！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試鏡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又能參加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  優香上次…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  吃一塹長一智  這次肯定能跳得完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始六點四十三分發車的駛往熱海的Resort21普通電車開始檢票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  出發吧  朝著我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  你今天不是沒有摔跤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到重新編排的部分優香會跳錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事  你別那麼傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是紗季要轉學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想這次能成功的話  我們就能出道然後永遠在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是都說過了嘛  就算轉學再來參加試鏡也是小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空塔真高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得不怎麼讓人感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  畢竟不能說是第一次看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是第二次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是賺了一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們昨天來過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的名字和凜家的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和我說過全日本有許多和我們家名字一樣的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們昨天觸碰到的石頭吧  這難道是神石？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這也是神石的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字一樣的神社裏肯定會有神石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  但真可能是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全日本到底有多少塊神石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們沒碰過這塊神石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有寫神社裏所有的石頭都是從神石上分離出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了讓我再重來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊  夏海  好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們覺得神石實現了我們什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我們在昨天傍晚許下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人能在一起的時間只剩一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我們許下的願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暑假也能延長就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會結束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那這個願望要怎樣才能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  現在就已經實現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  所以今天還是昨天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那現在呢  我們的願望已經實現了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  起的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很完美  絕對沒問題了  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說已經無計可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換心情  轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像的壓力會很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要好好釋放一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要約個時間碰頭沒想到意外的難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為鈴你很忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得鈴你從以前開始就很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候覺得是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明每天從早到晚和朋友在一起也只有那時候才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在夏海她們應該在參加試鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們在一個奇怪的地方參加試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  明天去打網球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  四個人一起打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒  明天打網球啊  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高科技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的凜偶爾會有讓人擔心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要讓我家的大樹也帶一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得奇怪嗎  她們說過要讓這個試鏡成為和紗季最後的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間有件事讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你們還想繼續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼時候回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你什麼時候回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  本來就是從凜的媽媽那裏得知神石的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說凜的媽媽也是過來人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:13:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  總之不能這樣一直下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向神石許的願是不能取消  也不能用別的願望來覆蓋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去東京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去試鏡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想  只要我們做完所有想做的事  說不定就能解除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功  了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  不能睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能順利解除就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  試鏡也沒有出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就只有我們重來了好幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子說她知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓暑假終止的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概讓一切都結束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  要和這力量  和神石給於我們的奇跡說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說再見？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想這一定就是媽媽所說的「回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就兵貴神速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再等下去也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有點寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香當然是很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白夏海的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不會結束的事情是無法成為回憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  優香  凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的給了我一個非常美麗的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想讓它成為我最美的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前每次都是第一個的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記這個夏天發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記和大家一起度過的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記這個珍貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是結束還是沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  來試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸摸神石看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  到了明天就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天結束了的話  明天就來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  早點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從這裏開始的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  你發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們的奇跡和暑假就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行回來之後  好像心情平靜了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是托了夏海的福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有空也一定要來島上玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  我到祐介那裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樹  有見到夏海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說到凜那裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季姐姐也一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了 試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  但是只要再去參加就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱乎乎的  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好遲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在幫忙搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來許「希望紗季不要搬家」的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神石已經不會創造奇跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個願望不是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們四個人永遠都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
